Mark VAUGHN v. McKISSICK PRODUCTS CORPORATION et al. No. 7340. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. May 15, 1963. Willard F. Kitts, Albuquerque, N. M., for appellant. Jackson G. Akin, Albuquerque, N. M., and Hall & Sublett, Tulsa, Okl., for ap-pellees.

Before MURRAH, Chief Judge, and LEWIS, Circuit Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed May 15, 1963, pursuant to stipulation of the parties.
